display_long_description:
Who am I?
When I woke up, a mysterious voice spoke to me...

"You, use the power of the Phoenix Clan."

Anyway, it seems that the only way I can survive is to board the high-speed spaceship in front of me and annihilate the approaching spacenoids...

[How to play]
Use the central controller to control your fighter plane.

High performance laser with auto-aiming and auto-tracking!
The best of three types, Straight, Wide, and Strong, is automatically selected depending on the enemy situation.
If you destroy enemy planes in succession, you will achieve a combo and get extra points.
When you are not operating the game, a strengthened barrier will be activated and you will be invincible.

Defeat enemies and absorb energy balls to level up.
Level up and strengthen your character by selecting Phoenix, Bullet, Laser, or Battery.
Touch the Phoenix that appears in the top right corner of the Level Up Select to perform an invincible attack for a certain period of time.
Touch the Bullet that appears in the top right corner of the Level Up Select to perform a bullet barrage attack.

Energy bonuses will appear every time you reach a certain level.
Absorb energy to get points.
Guide the bullets well, stick them together to make them bigger and get a high score.

Your fighter plane will not take damage even if it collides with an enemy.
It will take damage if its altitude drops below 0m.

Copyright 2024- Nam Creations
